description: Coor Service Management Holding AB engages in the provision of facility management services. The company is headquartered in Kista, Stockholm and currently employs 8,937 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2015-06-16. The firm specializes in integrated facility management (IFM), including both soft and hard kinds of services, such as cleaning, reception, catering, post and parcel, strategic consulting and others. The services can be offered as single or package. The firm operates across Sweden, Finland, Norway and Denmark.
naicsSector: Administrative and Support and Waste Management and Remediation Services
